===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Leon (Masters)}}
Leon forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Leon|Charizard}}, {{TP|Leon|Eternatus}}, {{form|Calyrex|Ice Rider}} {{p|Calyrex}}, {{p|Dragapult}}, and {{p|Seismitoad}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Charizard is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing, while his Eternatus is capable of [[Eternamax]]ing, and his Dragapult is capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Leon became a playable sync pair on February 26, 2021.

Leon has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

